    13Рєњ## ­ЪџЁ Quick start
    15Рєњ1.  **Create the application.**
    16Рєњ
    17Рєњ    Use [degit](https://github.com/Rich-Harris/degit) to get this template.
    18Рєњ
    19Рєњ    ```shell
    20Рєњ    # Clone the template
    21Рєњ    npx degit chromaui/intro-storybook-react-template taskbox
    22Рєњ    ```
    23Рєњ
    24Рєњ1.  **Install the dependencies.**
    25Рєњ
    26Рєњ    Navigate into your new siteРђЎs directory and install the necessary dependencies.
    27Рєњ
    28Рєњ    ```shell
    29Рєњ    # Navigate to the directory
    30Рєњ    cd taskbox/
    31Рєњ
    32Рєњ    # Install the dependencies
    33Рєњ    yarn
    34Рєњ    ```
    35Рєњ
    36Рєњ1.  **Open the source code and start editing!**
    37Рєњ
    38Рєњ    Open the `taskbox` directory in your code editor of choice and building your first component!
    39Рєњ
    40Рєњ1.  **Browse your stories!**
    41Рєњ
    42Рєњ    Run `yarn storybook` to see your component's stories at `http://localhost:6006`
