    56Рєњ    РћюРћђРћђ package.json
    57Рєњ    РћюРћђРћђ yarn.lock
    58Рєњ    РћюРћђРћђ vite.config.js
    59Рєњ    РћћРћђРћђ README.md
    60Рєњ
    61Рєњ1.  **`.storybook`**: This directory contains Storybook's [configuration](https://storybook.js.org/docs/react/configure/overview) files.
    62Рєњ
    63Рєњ2.  **`node_modules`**: This directory contains all of the modules of code that your project depends on (npm packages).
    64Рєњ
    65Рєњ3.  **`public`**: This directory will contain the development and production build of the site.
    66Рєњ
    67Рєњ4.  **`src`**: This directory will contain all of the code related to what you will see on your application.
    68Рєњ
    69Рєњ5.  **`.gitignore`**: This file tells git which files it should not track or maintain during the development process of your project.
    70Рєњ
    71Рєњ6.  **`.index.html`**: This is the HTML page that is served when generating a development or production build.
    72Рєњ
    73Рєњ7.  **`LICENSE`**: The template is licensed under the MIT licence.
